---
title: "US12 — Record and manage workouts"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ActiveWorkoutScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>StartWorkoutSession / EndWorkoutSession
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>WorkoutGateway → Supabase
  A->>B: tap START
  B->>C: start(type)
  C->>G: insert workout_sessions
  A->>B: tap END → Save & Finish
  B->>C: end()
  C->>G: rpc end_workout_session(metrics)
  note right of G: atomic - duration, calories,<br/>XP, streak, level-up post
  G-->>C: xp_gained, streak, leveled_up
  C-->>B: summary result
  B-->>A: Workout complete (+XP, streak)
